			<td align="center"><font class="lt5"><b>Uso de óleo essencial de alho e isotiocianato de alila contra [e]lt;i[e]rt;escherichia coli[e]lt;/i[e]rt; o 157:h7 em linguiça suína frescal</b></font>
			<BR>
			<font class="lt4"><i>Garlic essential oil and allyl isothiocyanate against [e]lt;/i[e]rt;escherichia colie. coli[e]lt;i[e]rt; o 157: h7 in fresh sausage</i></font>
			<BR>
			</td>
